QueryText: DECLARE $param3 AS Text; DECLARE $param4 AS Uint64; SELECT t3.id, t3.code, t3.description FROM table_delta t3 WHERE t3.code=$param3 ORDER BY t3.updated_at DESC LIMIT $param4
SELECT t4.id, t4.region, t4.population FROM table_epsilon t4 WHERE t4.region IN ('North', 'South', 'East', 'West') AND t4.active = true
SELECT AVG(t5.value), t5.category FROM table_zeta t5 GROUP BY t5.category HAVING AVG(t5.value) > 100
